e/version.json\"}, \"name\": \"Bash\", \"type\": \"tool_use\"}, {\"id\": \"toolu_01Taf5MV9Xm6EHMTvt6XmxYC\", \"input\": {\"command\": \"jq keys /imbue_addons/version.json\", \"description\": \"Show keys in /imbue_addons/version.json\"}, \"name\": \"Bash\", \"type\": \"tool_use\"}, {\"id\": \"toolu_01NEdMRwn7MsGm4K6kyyry6t\", \"input\": {\"command\": \"grep unknown /imbue_addons/version.json\", \"description\": \"Search for 'unknown' in version.json\"}, \"name\": \"Bash\", \"type\": \"tool_use\"}, {\"id\": \"toolu_013DB49huGqRwtEbPSLrk4r6\", \"input\": {\"command\": \"cat /hello_sculptor.txt\", \"description\": \"Display hello_sculptor.txt contents\"}, \"name\": \"Bash\", \"type\": \"tool_use\"}], \"role\": \"assistant\"}], \"model\": \"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 1.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929", "id": "msg_01UVrqnVzUk3JR4MKcVXgDu2", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Here are the results:\n\n**Environment Information:**\n- **Current directory**: `/code`\n- **Current user**: `devuser`\n- **Files in /code**: Dockerfile, README.md, data/, pyproject.toml, src/, test_dummy.py\n- **PATH**: `/venv/bin:/usr/local/sbin:/usr/local/bin:/usr/sbin:/usr/bin:/sbin:/bin:/imbue_addons/agent_path_extension_bin/`\n\n**Executable Locations:**\n- **bash**: `/imbue_addons/agent_path_extension_bin/bash`\n- **python**: `/venv/bin/python`\n- **uv**: `/venv/bin/uv`\n- **git**: Not found (command errored)\n\n**Version Files:**\n- **/imbue/version.json keys**: `_IMBUE_BUILT_AT_LAST_COMMIT_DATE`, `_IMBUE_BUILT_AT_LAST_COMMIT_TIMESTAMP`, `_IMBUE_BUILT_AT_TIMESTAMP`, `_IMBUE_BUILT_BY_USER`, `_IMBUE_BUILT_FROM_GIT_BRANCH`, `_IMBUE_BUILT_FROM_GIT_HASH`, `_IMBUE_BUILT_ON_HOSTNAME`\n- **/imbue_addons/version.json keys**: `built_at_timestamp`, `built_from_sculptor_git_hash`, `built_from_sculptor_version`\n- **grep \"unknown\"**: No matches found\n\n**/hello_sculptor.txt**: \"Hello Imbue!\""}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 6, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 5285, "cache_read_input_tokens": 11124, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 5285, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 395, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": \"Please write a 5-10 word title for the following conversation:\\n\\nUser: Warmup\\n\\nClaude: I'm ready to help you search through your codebase! I'm Claude Code, Anthropic's file search specialist.\\n\\nI can assist you with:\\n\\n1. **Finding files** - Using glob patterns to locate files by name, extension, or path\\n2. **Searching code** - Using regex patterns to find specific content within files\\n3. **Reading files** - Viewing the contents of files you're interested in\\n4. **File operations** - Listing directories, checking file structures\\n\\nJust let me know what you're looking for in your codebase at `/code`, and I'll help you navigate it efficiently.\\n\\nWhat would you like to search for?\\n\\nRespond with the title for the conversation and nothing else.\", \"role\": \"user\"}], \"model\": \"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 0.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-haiku-4-5-20251001", "id": "msg_01R3dVqrtoMVi6wepBBHPpCg", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Claude Code Search Assistant Warmup Session"}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 216, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 0, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 11, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
